A baby boy‚ believed to be just two months old‚ was found on New Year's Day at a bus stop on 3rd Avenue in The Hill‚ Johannesburg. ER24 said its paramedics found the baby in the evening‚ wrapped in a blanket at the bus stop. He had a low body temperature but was otherwise unharmed. "Paramedics quickly warmed the boy and later handed him over to the relevant authorities for further investigations‚" said ER24.